  <arm_group>
    <arm_group_label>1</arm_group_label>
    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>Day 1 hyperinsulinemic euglycemic clamps with either 0.2 mg fludrocortisone, 0.75 mg Dexamethasone, or both given orally before each morning and afternoon clamp. Day 2 hyperinsulinemic hypoglycemic glucose clamp.</description>
  </arm_group>
  <arm_group>
    <arm_group_label>2</arm_group_label>
    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>Fludrocortisone will be administered in doses of 0.05mg, 0.1mg and 0.2 mg form at the start of each clamp period on day 1. Dexamethasone will be administered orally in the doses of 0.18 mg, 0.375mg and 0.75mg doses. The combination of the 0.05mg fludrocortisone and 0.18mg dexamethasone and 0.1mg of fludrocortisone and 0.375 mg doses will be administered at the start of each day 1 clamp period. Day 2 90 minutes of moderate exercise.</description>
  </arm_group>
